vanillaonfire-connect
=====================

Vanilla2 JsConnect Module for CI-Bonfire

Setting Up.
 - Install Vanilla
 - Download Vanilla JS Connect from http://vanillaforums.org/addon/jsconnect-plugin
 - move the helper file to bonfire/application/helpers/vanilla
 - edit config/config.php to change your clientID and secret accordingly

 Enjoy!
